title: First Cow (2019)
summary: A skilled cook has traveled west and joined a group of fur trappers in Oregon, though he only finds true connection with a Chinese immigrant also seeking his fortune. Soon the two collaborate on a successful business.

title: Fellini Satyricon (1969)
summary: A series of disjointed mythical tales set in first century Rome.

title: Sátántangó (1994)
summary: On the eve of a large payment, residents of a collapsing collective farm see their plans turn into desolation when they discover that Irimiás, a former co-worker who they thought was dead, is returning to the community.
